"currencyservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["emailservice-2", "productcatalogservice-0", "checkoutservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["shippingservice-1", "frontend-1", "emailservice-0", "currencyservice-2", "adservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["redis-cart-0", "recommendationservice-0", "productcatalogservice-2", "paymentservice-0", "cartservice-2", "adservice-2"]}, "available_metric_names": ["client_error_ratio", "cpu_usage", "error_ratio", "node_cpu_usage_rate", "node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes", "pod_cpu_usage", "rrt", "rrt_max"], "log_analysis_findings": "基于收集到的日志数据，我现在进行分析。从异常时间段内的日志可以看出，这是一个明显的故障注入场景。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"stress\", \"AdService--stress\", \"byteman\", \"chaos_mesh\", \"TriggerThread\", \"StressHelper\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"adservice服务正在遭受stress类型的故障注入攻击，通过byteman和chaos_mesh框架执行CPU压力测试\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Rule.execute called for AdService--stress-1749718971_0:0 (出现155次), AdService--stress-1749718971 execute() (出现155次)\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**分析要点**:\n1. **明确的故障注入模式**: 所有日志都来自adservice服务，且包含`AdService--stress`标签，表明这是针对adservice的压力测试故障注入\n2. **技术栈识别**: 使用了`byteman`和`chaos_mesh`框架，这是常见的混沌工程工具\n3. **执行模式**: 日志显示大量线程创建和执行，表明正在进行CPU压力测试\n4. **时间一致性**: 故障注入时间段与用户报告的系统异常时间段完全吻合\n\n这明显是一个人为的故障注入实验，目的是测试系统在CPU压力下的稳定性。", "metric_analysis_findings": "```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"pod_cpu_usage\",\n    \"client_error_ratio\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"rrt\",\n    \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\",\n    \"node_cpu_usage_rate\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"Pod CPU usage increased significantly (pod_cpu_usage: 0.0 to 0.6, change_ratio: 2.0)\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_cpu_usage median increased from 0.0 to 0.6 with a change ratio of 2.0\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Client error ratio and error ratio spiked (client_error_ratio: 0.0 to 1.51, error_ratio: 0.0 to 1.51)\",\n      \"evidence\": \"client_error_ratio and error_ratio p99 increased from 0.0 to 1.51 with a change ratio of 2.0\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"Maximum response time (rrt_max) increased (4834.0 to 6131.0, change_ratio: 0.2366)\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max median increased from 4834.0 to 6131.0 with a change ratio of 0.2366\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-07\",\n      \"reason\": \"Node memory available decreased (node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes: 9347688448.0 to 8969801728.0, change_ratio: 0.0413) and CPU usage increased (node_cpu_usage_rate: 20.72 to 27.39, change_ratio: 0.2775)\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes decreased and node_cpu_usage_rate increased\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "trace_analysis_findings": "根据收集到的链路追踪数据，以下是分析结果：\n\n### 关键发现\n1. **延迟指标 (`rrt_max`)**:\n   - `checkoutservice->cartservice`: 正常平均耗时 2495.93ms，异常时段平均耗时 30710.5ms（延迟倍数 12.3x）。\n   - `cartservice->redis`: 正常平均耗时 1739.74ms，异常时段平均耗时 17804.67ms（延迟倍数 10.2x）。\n   - `checkoutservice->shippingservice`: 正常平均耗时 231.72ms，异常时段平均耗时 1210.0ms（延迟倍数 5.2x）。\n   - `checkoutservice->emailservice`: 正常平均耗时 699.97ms，异常时段平均耗时 1913.0ms（延迟倍数 2.7x）。\n\n2. **错误状态 (`error_ratio`)**:\n   - 未检测到明确的错误状态码组合，但延迟显著增加可能暗示服务性能问题或资源瓶颈。\n\n3. **调用关系**:\n   - `checkoutservice->cartservice` 和 `cartservice->redis` 的延迟倍数最高，表明 `cartservice` 和 `redis` 可能是问题的根源。\n\n### 假设分析\n- **根因组件**: `cartservice` 和 `redis`。\n  - **原因**: `rrt_max` 显著增加。\n  - **证据**: `cartservice` 的延迟倍数高达 12.3x，而 `redis` 的延迟倍数也达到 10.2x，表明 `redis` 可能是 `cartservice` 性能下降的根源。\n\n- **次要影响组件**: `shippingservice` 和 `emailservice`。\n  - **原因**: `rrt_max` 增加。\n  - **证据**: 这些服务的延迟倍数较低，可能是由于 `checkoutservice` 的请求堆积导致。\n\n### 输出结果\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"checkoutservice->cartservice\",\n    \"cartservice->redis\",\n    \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->emailservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"延迟倍数 12.3x（正常 2495.93ms，异常 30710.5ms）\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"延迟倍数 10.2x（正常 1739.74ms，异常 17804.67ms）\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 下一步建议\n1. **检查 `redis` 资源使用情况**（如 CPU、内存、网络带宽）。\n2. **分析 `cartservice` 的日志**，确认是否存在与 `redis` 交互的异常。\n3. **监控 `checkoutservice` 的请求队列**，确认是否因下游服务延迟导致请求堆积。"}
